fix: add static data fallback for article detail page

ArticleComponent was calling postService.getPostBySlug() without any
fallback — when the backend returns 404 (empty database), it showed
"文章不存在". Now it falls back to static content.generated.ts data,
matching the Blog list page behavior.

- Import STATIC_POSTS and staticToPost converter from blog component
- On API error, search static posts by slug
- Static content (already HTML) is rendered directly, markdown goes
  through MarkdownRendererService
- SEO meta tags also applied on fallback path

